divs: Sighting DetailsWe were in the pool. One guy said look and pointed south. we all watched as a solid chevron shaped flying object flw silently almost directly over our head snd continued northbound till out of sight. We thought at first it was a flock of geese but it had no sound and no movement it was solid. Someonw said it looked like a glider but it was dark out. Someone tho0ught it might be a drone from the 29 Palms Air Base but again it had no lights and was completely silent. We were pretty confused .. noone could come up with a plausible explaination for what we had witnessed. We decided it was definately unidentified..but dont know much other than that.
